<h1>
Control flow
</h1>
<hr class=top>

In IVR, control flow--at the highest level--is affected both by
<ul>
<li> previous input,
<li> dialog events, and
<li> by important asynchronous events
</ul>

<br>

VXML must clearly express
high-level  control flow 
<br>
<br>

